# AI-tool-specific outputs are generated from .rulesync/ via `rulesync generate`.
# Source of truth lives in .rulesync/. All AI-tool outputs (root-level CLAUDE.md
# and AGENTS.md included) are generated by `rulesync generate` and gitignored;
# the canonical content lives in .rulesync/rules/CLAUDE.md. Run
# `rulesync generate -t '*' -f '*'` after cloning to populate locally.
.memsearch/
.claude/
.mcp.json
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
.github/copilot-instructions.md
.gemini/
GEMINI.md
